File mosml/utility/README

dosedit         explains one way to use Moscow ML and an editor under 
                plain MS DOS

emacs           explains how to use Moscow ML under Emacs, with 
                Matthew Morley's sml-mode

MosML.ico       Moscow ML icon for Windows'95

sml-mode-3.3b   Matthew Morley's Emacs sml-mode version 3.3b, including
                customization for Moscow ML and Emacs Info documentation.  
                Available from http://www.scs.leeds.ac.uk/mjm/sml-mode/.
                Documentation in HTML and Postscript at:
                http://www.scs.leeds.ac.uk/mjm/sml-mode/sml-mode.html

                A more recent version (requires Emacs 20) is at 
                ftp://rum.cs.yale.edu/pub/monnier/sml-mode/
